No. 11A480. Reginald Brooks, Applicant v. Ohio. 565 U.S. 1047, 132 S. Ct. 608,

181 L. Ed. 2d 445,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 8291. November 15, 2011.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death, presented to Justice Kagan, and by her referred to the Court, denied.

Same case below, 130 Ohio St. 3d 1432, 957 N.E.2d 37.
